## Tech Stack & Key Dependencies

### Frontend
- **Framework**: React Native 0.81.5 with Expo SDK 54
- **Routing**: Expo Router v6 (file-based routing)
- **Language**: TypeScript 5.9
- **Navigation**: Bottom Tabs (`@react-navigation/bottom-tabs`) + Stack
- **State Management**: React Context (ThemeContext) + local state via hooks
- **AR/3D**: `expo-gl`, `expo-camera`, `three.js` (v0.166)
- **AI/ML**: `@tensorflow/tfjs`, `@tensorflow-models/coco-ssd`
- **UI**: Custom design system in `components/ui/theme.ts`
- **Networking**: Custom `apiClient.ts` service
- **Storage**: `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage`

### Backend
- **Runtime**: Node.js with ES Modules (`"type": "module"`)
- **Framework**: Express.js 4
- **Database**: MongoDB via Mongoose 8
- **AI**: Google Generative AI SDK (`@google/generative-ai`)
- **Auth**: JWT (`jsonwebtoken`) + bcryptjs
- **Security**: Helmet, CORS, express-rate-limit
- **Monitoring**: Sentry (`@sentry/node`), Morgan logger
- **Testing**: Jest + Supertest

